HANTAVIRUS - BRAZIL (MINAS GERAIS)
**************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
<http://www.fas.org/promed/ahead>
See Also
Hantavirus infection - Brazil (Sao Paulo state)(05) 980615204518
Date: Wed 16 Sep 1998
From: Promed-port@usa.healthnet.org
Source: O Estado de Sao Paulo (print edition)

A case of hantavirus pulmonary syndrome has been notified from
Uberlandia, Minas Gerais. This is the first confirmed case from that
state.
The confirmation was made by the Instituto Adolfo Lutz, reference
laboratory of the State Secretary of Health of Sao Paulo.
[ Uberlandia is not very far from Guariba, Sao Paulo State, where 2
cases of HPS have already occurred in 1998, and the area is
ecologically similar - ProMED-PORT Mod.LJS
------------------
[Portuguese original
Foi notificado um caso de febre hemorragica com sindrome
pulmonar, causada por hantavirus, em Uberlandia, Minas
Gerais.
Este e o primeiro caso confirmado de Minas Gerais.
A confirmacao foi feita no Instituto Adolfo Lutz, laboratorio
de referencia da Secretaria Estadual da Saude de Sao Paulo.
[Uberlandia nao e' muito distante de Guariba, SP, aonde
ocorreram 2 casos neste ano [1998 e apresenta caracteristicas
ecologicas semelhantes - ljs
................................................ jw
